**Offer Recipient** | Extra Miscellaneous

__Basics__
The Cerberus can send an offer to someone each day, granting them access to the offer channel where they can communicate with the Cerberus and select the option to sell their soul for protection.

__Details__
During the day the Cerberus may select a player to send an offer of protection to. The following night the player will be added to the offer channel and will leave at the start of the following day. In the offer channel. The recipient may accept or ignore the offer, but accepting the offer of protection is immediate and cannot be changed.
